# The repo root .gitignore has a blanket `lib/` (Python-venv boilerplate,
# kept for a future Fas 3+ Python service per docs/adr/0003) that also
# unintentionally matches SvelteKit's own `src/lib/` convention directory
# here -- un-ignore it explicitly rather than touching the shared root file.
!src/lib/
!src/lib/**
